    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This specimen represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance, maintained to an exacting standard. The flat-six powerplant features integrated dry-sump lubrication and a reinforced valvetrain, delivering linear power through a precision six-speed close-ratio manual transmission. The drivetrain is complemented by a mechanical limited-slip differential and an active suspension management system that ensures neutral handling characteristics. Braking performance is anchored by four-piston monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors, showing zero signs of thermal cycling. With a flawless factory finish and a chassis free of oxidative stress, this turn-key example is ready for the most discerning collector.",
